UNICEF Rest Extra
=================

Django package that handles includes rest framework extras


Installation
------------

.. code-block:: bash

    pip install unicef-restlib


Setup
-----

Add ``unicef_restlib`` to ``INSTALLED_APPS`` in settings

.. code-block:: bash

    INSTALLED_APPS = [
        ...
        'unicef_restlib',
    ]


